item.title: CVE-2022-4024|2024-08-03T01:27:54.143Z -- unknown -- registration%20forms
item.description: The Registration Forms WordPress plugin before 3.8.1.3 does not have authorisation and CSRF when deleting users via an init action handler, allowing unauthenticated attackers to delete arbitrary users (along with their posts)
